      "span_text": "The association of DNA to DOPE/DODAB (dioleoylphosphatidylethanolamine and dimethyldioctadecylammonium bromide) unilamellar vesicles investigated by Tr-SANS with a time resolution from one to several seconds  reveals a multistep process."
